OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775650289
OL,3,CCCTV footage shows moment arsonist
OL,4,Cstarts fire beneath block of flats
OL,6,FCCTV footage shows the moment an
OL,7,Farsonist started a rubbish fire
OL,8,Fbeneath a block of flats in Chatham.
OL,10,FMichelle Sutcliffe deliberately set a
OL,11,Fpile of rubbish alight in the parking
OL,12,Farea beneath Carton House in New Road
OL,13,Fin the early hours of Saturday 13
OL,14,FDecember 2025.
OL,16,FThe 40-year-old set the fire between
OL,17,Ftwo parked cars, which quickly began
OL,18,Fto spread after she walked away.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
