PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775650289
OL,3,CCCTV footage shows moment arsonist
OL,4,Cstarts fire beneath block of flats
OL,6,FIt caused extensive damage to both
OL,7,Fvehicles and caused light fixtures to
OL,8,Ffall from the ceiling of the parking
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FResidents were inside their homes at
OL,12,Fthe time.
OL,14,FSutcliffe was arrested on 19 December
OL,15,Fand later charged with arson with
OL,16,Frecklessness as to whether life was
OL,17,Fendangered.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
