PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775650289
OL,3,CCCTV footage shows moment arsonist
OL,4,Cstarts fire beneath block of flats
OL,6,FThe 40-year-old, of Lester Road,
OL,7,FChatham, pleaded guilty and was
OL,8,Fsentenced at Maidstone Crown Court on
OL,9,FThursday 26 March to two years and two
OL,10,Fmonths' imprisonment.
OL,12,FInvestigating officer Police Constable
OL,13,FEvie Cousins said: "Sutcliffe's
OL,14,Freckless and thoughtless behaviour
OL,15,Fcaused significant financial damage
OL,16,Fand created real fear among residents
OL,17,Fas the fire spread.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
