OL,3,CCCTV footage shows moment arsonist
OL,4,Cstarts fire beneath block of flats
OL,6,F"It is fortunate that no one was
OL,7,Finjured, as fires of this nature can
OL,8,Fescalate rapidly. Sutcliffe must now
OL,9,Fface the consequences of her actions."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
